                  <additions>
                    <list>
                      <item xml:id = "a1">
                        <desc>
                          <locus target = "#iv #iir #iiv"/> <foreign xml:lang = "gez">አስማት፡</foreign> prayer against evil spirits, damaged with incipit:
                            <foreign xml:lang = "gez">
                              ..አጋንንት፡ መግረሬ፡ [ፀ]ር፡ በከም፡ ተሰዱ፡ [..]ማሙኪር፡ ባሪ[ያ፡] ወመቃውዜ፡ ዛ[ር፡] ወዛራትል ሥራየ፡ [ጉ]ዳሌ፡ ወጠፍንት፡ ነሀቢ፡ ወቄደር፡ ባርያ፡ ወነገርጋር፡...
                            </foreign>
                        </desc>
                      </item>
                      <item xml:id = "a2">
                        <desc>
                          <locus target = "#40v"/> Fragment of a prayer to God, with incipit:
                          <foreign xml:lang = "gez">
                            ሰ፡ ሕይወት፡ ወሰላም፡ እንዘ፡ ይጸወኑ፡፡ብከ፡ ፍ..፡..ይማኖ..፡ ንጽሐ፡ ወትእግሥተ፡ ፍቅረ፡ ወኂሩተ፡...
                          </foreign>
                        </desc>
                      </item>
                      <item xml:id = "a3">
                        <desc>
                          <locus target = "#51v #52r #52v"/> Prayer against evil spirits. Incomplete at the beginning and at the end, with incipit:
                          <foreign xml:lang = "gez">
                            ..እመሂ፡ በመዓልት፡ ወእመሂ፡ በሌሊት፡ እመሂ፡ በሠርክ፡ ወእመሂ፡ በጽልመት፡ ወበብርሃን፡ እመሂ፡ በቀትር፡ ወበሰአት፡ በኵሉ፡ ጊዜ፡ ወበኵሉ፡ ወርኅ፡ ኢትቅረቡ፡ ኃቤየ፡...
                          </foreign>
                        </desc>
                      </item>
                      <item xml:id = "a4">
                        <desc type = "ScribalNoteCommissioning">Copied for <foreign xml:lang = "gez">ሰፎንያስ፡</foreign>, <locus target = "#50v"/></desc>
                      </item>
                      <item xml:id = "a5">
